rows.label: tlk45350171_02_msg0001
rows.name:
This world is a cruel, empty place.
There is no joy. Only despair.

rows.label: tlk45350171_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Fan-sama has passed away...
Gazing upon her was all that kept
my soul at ease...

rows.label: tlk45350171_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I hear my homeland of Superbia is
forming a peace treaty with Invidia.

rows.label: tlk45350171_02_msg0004
rows.name:
No doubt the result of some higher-up
seeing Fan-sama's smile and realizing
the futility of conflict. Oh, Fan-sama...
